sql_query.sql: SELECT "user_ips".* FROM "user_ips" WHERE "user_ips"."user_id" = $1 ORDER BY "user_ips"."user_id" ASC LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "blocks" WHERE "blocks"."account_id" = $1 AND "blocks"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "follows" WHERE "follows"."account_id" = $1 AND "follows"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT "tags".* FROM "tags" WHERE LOWER("tags"."name") = LOWER('doloremque21') ORDER BY "tags"."id" ASC LIMIT $1

SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "statuses_tags" ON "statuses_tags"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "mentions" ON "mentions"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" WHERE "statuses"."account_id" = $1 AND ("statuses"."visibility" IN ($2, $3) OR "mentions"."account_id" = $4) AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses_tags"."tag_id" = $5 GROUP BY "statuses"."id" ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "statuses_tags" ON "tags"."id" = "statuses_tags"."tag_id" WHERE "statuses_tags"."status_id" = $1 AND "tags"."id" = $2 LIMIT $3
